data.description: Check out this opportunity to own a great townhome in the popular subdivision of Rockwood Villas! Not only do you have great amenities like a community pool, you're close to the University of Florida (Go Gators!), and all the best that downtown Gainesville has to offer. The property itself features three bedrooms all with individual bathrooms, giving you nice privacy. There is one bedroom and bathroom downstairs with two additional bedrooms and bathrooms upstairs. This property has a screened porch addition, so it gives you some nice inside/outside space if you like spending time outside without the bugs! Some recent improvements include newer air conditioning and newer exterior roof on the porch. The property is perfect for anyone looking for a home or a potential investment property. This community does have a strong rental market as well. Schedule a showing today before it's gone!
